mil.nga.giat.geowave.core.ingest.local

Class LocalFileIngestDriver

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.core.ingest.local.AbstractLocalFileDriver<LocalFileIngestPlugin<?>,LocalIngestRunData>
      • mil.nga.giat.geowave.core.ingest.local.LocalFileIngestDriver

  • public class LocalFileIngestDriver
extends AbstractLocalFileDriver<LocalFileIngestPlugin<?>,LocalIngestRunData>
    This extends the local file driver to directly ingest data into GeoWave utilizing the LocalFileIngestPlugin's that are discovered by the system.
